<plot>When the famous local vigilante "The Suit" puts out a call for a sidekick, one ambitious young kid decides to apply for the job by creating a home video of his superhero talents. Whether it be a "rescue operation", "night stealth", "overcoming insurmountable odds", or "super strength", our young super-hero-in-training shows all of the enthusiasm, however none of the skill, required to be a super-hero. In this slapstick superhero comedy, enjoy the trials and pitfalls of training to become a superhero's sidekick.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?199036</url></doc>
